{"tid":526593,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[疑問]牛肉乾抄錯左車牌，洗唔洗交？","createTime":"2018-01-11T18:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T10:48:22.000Z","uid":12881,"like":173,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e40802882a1653027d3cea78124c75fc0cb5ab6d","tid":526593,"uid":12881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n夜媽媽揸車急尿就放低架車係橫街<br />\n前後唔夠三分鐘就抄鳩左我架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有認命吧啦 督尿真心貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知返到屋企睇張牛肉乾<br />\n車牌AA1234(舉例)抄左AA234(舉例)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚到我仆街 字都抄漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依個情況應該可以偷雞唔洗交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d60ac36f9c05c74f04ab24958048c5ea576ae9","tid":526593,"uid":61367,"like":268,"dislike":2,"score":266,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"比番張牛肉乾人啦"},{"pid":"8ca87688f0426556ac67fbd976f1aeb8db1ca61d","tid":526593,"uid":110745,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:22:09.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"3a192f03643e841ff225a81a265bcaec302e0887","tid":526593,"uid":13645,"like":171,"dislike":3,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:22:45.000Z","msg":"車牌唔係寫你架車<br />\n點解要幫其他車交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5214b5f1d321b9fb876f6fb347fd4d3e947be40a","tid":526593,"uid":54181,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:22:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"308f0d88b4a8d52e179347c006f80d9a0767bf20","tid":526593,"uid":36478,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"rep