rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔撚洗找"},{"pid":"59c99368f0c3fdeb40ff7bcc74904013515a4fff","tid":526593,"uid":12881,"like":94,"dislike":5,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:53:28.000Z","msg":"我自己係google 做左少少research<br />\n<br />\n牛肉乾抄錯資料情況，非關鍵錯誤，仍要交罰款<br />\n<br />\n1) 其他資料岩，但電子繳費號碼日期錯，告票仍有效力<br />\nFYI: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090108/12062329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090108%2F12062329&d=NUlzduIIALC96qeNaTRxdmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=dee4ef28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090108%2F12062329&h=94af5b89\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090108/12062329</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 其他資料岩，但時間錯，而當時有不在場證據，可以撤銷告票。<br />\nFYI: <a href=\"http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2015/03/04/321606.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2015%2F03%2F04%2F321606.asp&d=NUlzduIIALC96qeNaTRxdmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6b0b08fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2015%2F03%2F04%2F321606.asp&h=90bbcdce\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2015/03/04/321606.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n3) 其他資料岩，但街道寫錯錯別字，仲認到該街名，告票仍有機會生效，但如果街道錯得太離譜，但可以撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n4）其他資料岩，但車牌好似小弟咁抄錯，其實毅進仔會抄埋行車證號碼，唔交都會寄到信去登記地址，但主動提出證據予中央交通組就可以撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n5) 違反交通規則，比鐵馬斷正，抄埋身份証，如非關鍵錯誤，告票仍然生效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時寫住咁多先，諗到再寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下有無巴絲分享下經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe337c015e59424c36822f1544c6d436aba911d","tid":526593,"uid":12881,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T19:00:05.000Z","msg":"少少筆誤 重post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己係google 做左少少research<br />\n<br />\n牛肉乾抄錯資料情況，非關鍵錯誤，仍要交罰款<br />\n<br />\n1) 其他資料岩，但電子繳費號碼日期錯，告票仍有效力<br />\nFYI: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090108/12062329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090108%2F12062329&d=NUlzduIIALC96qeNaTRxdmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=dee4ef28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090108%2F12062329&h=94af5b89\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090108/12062329</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 其他資料岩，但時間錯，而當時有不在場證據，可以撤銷告票。<br />\nFYI: <a href=\"http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2015/03/04/321606.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2015%2F03%2F04%2F321606.asp&d=NUlzduIIALC96qeNaTRxdmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6b0b08fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.stheadline.com%2Fdailynews%2Fcontent_hk%2F2015%2F03%2F04%2F321606.asp&h=90bbcdce\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.stheadline.com/dailynews/content_hk/2015/03/04/321606.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n3) 其他資料岩，但街道寫錯錯別字，仲認到該街名，告票仍有機會生效，但若街道錯得太離譜，仍可以撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n4）其他資料岩，但車牌好似小弟咁抄錯，其實毅進仔會抄埋行車證號碼，唔交都會寄信去登記地址，主動提出證據予中央交通組就應該可以撤銷。<br />\n<br />\n5) 違反交通規則，被鐵馬斷正，抄埋身分証，如非關鍵錯誤（錯時間地點車牌身分證），告票仍然生效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時寫住咁多先，諗到再寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下有無巴絲分享下經歷 同 點樣void到張票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d24bd1d6e6827b2a38f667933583527f5dd588","tid":526593,"uid":16058,"like":3,"dislike":58,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T20:38:04.000Z","msg":"$320就唔好搞咁多野啦 有時間打個電話去問下咪仲好"},{"pid":"e346c76a1def57e6702d05e4cf569e4c83d6b6bc","tid":526593,"uid":71342,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"c6d24bd1d6e6827b2a38f667933583527f5dd588","tid":526593,"uid":16058,"like":3,"dislike":58,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T20:38:04.000Z","msg":"$320就唔好搞咁多野啦 有時間打個電話去問下咪仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:28:58.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7045709ef0c329cea483d81ac974be1091c1f4be","tid":526593,"uid":72304,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"佢留俾你個record 錯，但佢自己mark 個record 可能啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想陰鳩你唔交都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e9189d5171357edddeb66b6a06b60daccc41f5","tid":526593,"uid":1159,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"efe337c015e59424c36822f1544c6d436aba911d","tid":526593,"uid":12881,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T19:00:05.000Z","msg":"少少筆誤 重post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己係google 做左少少research<br />\n<br />\n牛肉乾抄錯資料情況，非關鍵錯誤，仍要交罰款<br />\n<br />\n1) 其他資料岩，但電子繳費號碼日期錯，告票仍有效力<br />\nFYI: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090108/12062329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090108%2F12062329&d=NUlzduIIALC96qeNaTRxdmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3